When Dreamgirls premiered in late 1981, Jennifer Holliday had taken over the lead.
In 1981, Carter also took a role on television's The Misadventures of Sheriff Lobo, before landing the lead role of Nell Harper on the sitcom Gimme a Break!.
Gimme a Break! aired from 1981 to 1987.
In August 1987, after the cancellation of Gimme a Break!, Carter returned to the nightclub circuit with a five-month national tour with comedian Joan Rivers.
